N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 165.2 - Unclassified

State Regulations
"Unclassified" consists of potatoes which have not been
classified in accordance with any of the foregoing grades. The term
"unclassified" is not a grade within the meaning of these standards but is
provided as a designation to show that no grade has been applied to the
lot. Notes
